Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.75,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.81,0:00:23.34,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.81,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.89,0:00:31.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.49,0:00:40.70,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.70,0:00:50.44,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.04,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.11,0:00:55.31,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.95,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:07.42,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.20,0:01:16.90,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.43,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.57,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.65,0:01:28.55,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.96,0:01:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你跟她的保鏢動過手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.67,0:01:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息真靈通啊\N不過，我決定下次再分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.64,0:01:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼報告？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.81,0:01:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男爵夫人的命令是\N不管任務成功或失敗都要報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣，他們都不可能\N逃出這個封棄世界大陸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不必我多說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以感情用事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.49,0:02:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校竟然會說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除掉將會毀滅世界的劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡只想著這件事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#02 半桶水騎士的進行曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.94,0:03:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？過得還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.44,0:03:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥，有山賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是山賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以分點好東西給我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.46,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醃菜好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是個乖女孩啊，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那邊那個年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖把所有東西留下來\N這樣會對你比較好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼，你要自討苦吃我可不管喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你們這種\N危害人們生活的不正當行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下絕對不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要代替瑪烏傑魯神制裁你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那是你們的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有完全晾乾才收起來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下可是只穿乾衣服的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿在身上就會乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半乾的在車裡面晾啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車裡面會很臭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.81,0:04:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我不穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且妳啊...\N咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就請多保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛看到你們好像很困擾的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...大概會去某個城鎮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在旅行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.79,0:05:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我陪你們走一段路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒就好，一會兒就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以好好聊一下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.57,0:05:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請以結婚為前提，跟我交...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙突然說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？我在求婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是雷歐波爾特史科魯普斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克領領主\N史科魯普斯男爵家的長子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，從那麼遠的地方來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做武術修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是進入琥珀騎士團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.92,0:06:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀騎士團？\N你是指那個宮廷騎士團嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對，就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊邦王國騎士中的菁英集團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最強的武裝集團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，一點都沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們正在旅行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.71,0:07:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果把互許終身的年輕女孩\N丟在這種無法無天的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那將是史科魯普斯家\N世世代代的恥辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互許終身？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在通過這條道路之前\N就由我來保護妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.96,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點怪\N不過這個人看起來蠻有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡...真是個好名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很適合美麗的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看，有品味的人\N一聽就能聽得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪烏傑魯神啊\N感謝您賜給我這次相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，雷歐波爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.89,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的武術修行\N到底是在做些什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽過德伊魯巴雷特\N這個名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.06,0:07:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是琥珀騎士團的前副團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.27,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想向那位前輩請教騎士的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想靠關係走後門入團嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要戴著有色眼鏡看事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，挨罵了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.75,0:08:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷特在十五年前突然引退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.22,0:08:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種說法是他和當年\N廢棄公主的封印扯上關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時被廢棄公主詛咒\N使得身體狀況變差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詛...詛咒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是謠傳而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.07,0:08:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況是不是真有廢棄公主\N都還不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你們怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太耀眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來您在啊，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥...哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個像野貓一樣的丫頭\N到底哪裡好啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.01,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說全部也未免太...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂一見鍾情不就是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.65,0:09:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果硬要說個理由的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是氣質吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說她像野貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.23,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，她身上有種像貓一樣\N難以形容的堅強特質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.83,0:09:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你妹妹身上我感到一種\N不像平民而像是古老貴族的骨氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來游泳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，就是有點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不會游啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族和平民啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂也去擦擦身體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枉費雷歐還特地向她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果已經變成她的寵物了\N一，二...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.08,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去那位叫德伊魯的家\N看看好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.35,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於十五年前的事情\N我們只知道父親遺書裡寫的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人說不定知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心，放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始得先習慣水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的，看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡，妳看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在說這裡有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.45,0:11:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆，這裡有什麼東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，你這隻兩棲動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對湖的主人做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.97,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是住這附近的小孩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.67,0:11:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們稱為"龍"的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說那是龍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是用青蛙的遺傳資料\N替代了原本的外表吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.59,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個識別信號是\N系列編號7，葛羅莉亞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到變成那種狀況\N還能繼續運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須保護才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護那個人深愛的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管要花幾千、幾萬年...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她安息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要對她說一句"已經夠了"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有接到命令\N我們連入睡都不能自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:12:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在說明妳也無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想問啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們把湖的主人怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.15,0:13:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是對她說\N"妳已經可以休息了"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去休息了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個是在旅行途中嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這種鄉下地方有何貴幹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在找一位叫\N德伊魯巴雷特的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想見見這位傳說中的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德伊魯...什麼的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德伊魯巴雷特\N原本是王國的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國騎士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說在這邊有他的府邸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點緊張呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.24,0:14:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他身上真的有詛咒\N要怎麼辦啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有那種力量嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.01,0:14:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的有\N大概也是讓人發胖之類的詛咒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好"大"的府邸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去叫門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是巴雷特...先生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.15,0:15:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正以進入琥珀騎士團為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.78,0:15:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此想請巴雷特先生教導我\N什麼是騎士的精神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士的精神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想問這個你就白跑一趟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在只是個普通的鄉村大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時間追求那種無聊東西的話\N還不如去種種田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你說這是什麼話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐可是仰慕你才來的\N你怎麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你們自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是喔\N原來他是這種人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾啊，雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.52,0:16:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我還一直擔心\N你是不是變胖了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去了啦，你還在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，因為那邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.67,0:16:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是懸崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就請回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直聽父母說起您的事蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.29,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說您比誰都了解正義的意義\N是一位偉大的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都明白騎士的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你殺過人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.47,0:16:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是沒有反抗能力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺過一次你就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.34,0:17:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親手殺死一個你不憎恨也不厭惡\N又沒有抵抗能力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂騎士的精神根本就是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上沒有絕對的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.66,0:17:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你\N所謂的騎士精神是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的正義是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.83,0:17:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂，可不可以教教我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.69,0:17:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.06,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這顆蛋我要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是替我們平息湖泊主人的謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們並沒有做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.84,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中湖泊的主人是在\N魔王布拉寧的詛咒下受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.35,0:18:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想為祂做些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.49,0:18:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果我算是幫助了人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是向妳說謝謝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳就一定是做了好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.67,0:18:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你們見到德伊魯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見是見到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道為什麼\N他好像不願意談有關騎士的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他是有過痛苦的遭遇\N才不當騎士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.72,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是十五年前\N"聖葛林德的神喻"的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.33,0:19:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛出世的公主天生就命帶兇星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.60,0:19:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是生病還是詛咒\N就是所謂的廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.84,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他奉命解決那個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.65,0:19:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒想到那個可愛嬰兒\N實在讓人難以相信是不祥之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也有傳言說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女嬰被暗中救起\N還活在某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.94,0:19:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆，不要說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像說得太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.98,0:19:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼事情都有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就多體諒他一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.48,0:20:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點精神也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.86,0:20:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想成為一個夠格的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為琥珀騎士團的一員\N保護王國裡的每個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.03,0:20:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士的精神究竟是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:18.00,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.07,0:21:23.37,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.44,0:21:30.85,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.92,0:21:36.01,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:40.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.76,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.83,0:21:49.77,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.84,0:21:56.40,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.48,0:21:59.88,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.95,0:22:03.07,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.15,0:22:09.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.72,0:22:16.42,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.50,0:22:21.73,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
